<h5 id="subject_1122323">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;topic=126499.msg1122323#msg1122323" rel="nofollow">【Bestiary 3】突蟹龟（Tojanida）</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1122323'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1122323'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2021-07-07, 周三 17:25:25 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1122323_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1122323"><span style="font-size: 13pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>这种生物类似于乌龟与螃蟹组合，用鳍状肢代替了腿，有喙，还有两个钳子。</em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong>突蟹龟，CR5</strong></span></span><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>XP 1,600</strong></span><br>绝对中立 中型异界生物（跨位面亚种，水系亚种）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>先攻</strong></span> +1；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感官</strong></span> 全局视野，黑暗视觉60尺；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>察觉</strong></span> +14<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>防御</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>AC</strong></span>21，碰触12，措手不及 19（+1敏捷，+1闪避，+9天生）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>HP</strong></span>&nbsp; 51 (6d10+18)；<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>强韧</strong></span>+8，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>反射</strong></span>+6，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>意志</strong></span> +3<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>抗力</strong></span> 火10，电击10；<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>攻击</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>速度</strong></span>10尺，游泳90尺<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>近战</strong></span> 啮咬+9（1d6+3），2爪抓+9（1d6+3）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊攻击</strong></span>墨水云Ink Cloud<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>数据</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>力量</strong></span>16，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>敏捷</strong></span> 13，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>体质</strong></span> 17，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>智力</strong></span> 10，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感知</strong></span> 12，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>魅力</strong></span>9<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>BAB</strong></span> +6；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMB</strong></span> +9；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMD</strong></span> 21（29vs.绊摔）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>专长</strong></span> 盲斗，闪避，猛力攻击<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>技能</strong></span> 唬骗+5，逃脱+10，知识（位面）+9，察觉+14，表演（动作）+5，察言观色+10，隐匿+7，生存+7，游泳+11；种族调整+4察觉<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>语言</strong></span> 水族语<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>生态背景</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>环境</strong></span> 任何水中（水位面）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>组织</strong></span> 单独，成对，一群（3-6）或礼拜（1突蟹龟加上2-12名类人生物追随者）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>财宝</strong></span> 标准<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>墨水云 （Ink Cloud，Ex）：</strong></span>每分钟以一个自由动作，突蟹龟能喷出30尺半径的墨水云。这团墨水云提供完全隐蔽效果，并持续1分钟。如果在水外使用，墨水云变为30尺长的直线，并且该范围内的生物必须通过DC16的反射豁免，否则将目盲1轮。豁免DC基于体质。<br><br>突蟹龟是水位面上的奇异原住民，类似于巨大螃蟹和鳄龟的混合体。突蟹龟最初是纯粹的水元素，很久以前由于不明原因被束缚成奇怪的形态，并且不再知道它们最终如何才能恢复其纯净无形的状态。为了保住自己的尊严，怪诞的突蟹龟在水位面上追求着享乐主义的乐趣，尤其是食物的乐趣以及来自其它种族的崇拜。如果受到足够的尊重，他们会愿意交谈，并且表现出强大力量存在的先锋和使者的样子，即使在独自行动时也会经常喜欢伪装成这样。然而，当被激怒时，突蟹龟会成为可怕的对手，暴力和力量随着下巴嘎吱作响，钳子噼啪作响展现。<br>成年的突蟹龟大约6英尺长，重数百磅。当受到威胁时，突蟹龟可以将它的四肢大部分缩回到它的外壳中，这是她身体不可动摇的一部分。沿其边缘完全环绕着突蟹龟外壳的眼环使该生物极难被意外发现。突蟹龟因为发现气味与品尝是最迷人的两种感官而喜欢吃，但是实际上他们并不需要吃食物，而是通过贝壳的魔力直接从周围的奥术能量流中吸取养分。<br>突蟹龟有着被祝福（也有人说是诅咒）的极长种族记忆，游荡在无数世界的海洋和湖泊中，试图找到不寻常的身体乐趣和谈话，能够分散注意缓解他们因难以忍受回忆祖先经历而产生的倦怠和冷漠。尽管突蟹龟自己不明白记忆的负担，但冒险家和学者寻求突蟹龟回忆中的知识。<br><br><a href="https://imgtu.com/i/Rbn62R" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/07/07/Rbn62R.md.jpg" alt="" class="bbc_img"/></a><br><br>本来5月份就要翻完了，因为各种原因拖到现在，差不多马上可以解决完B3了<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Tojanida<br>This creature resembles a cross between a turtle and a crab, with flippers instead of legs, a snapping beak, and two pincers.<br>TOJANIDA CR 5<br>XP 1,600<br>N Medium outsider (extraplanar, water)<br>Init +1; Senses all-around vision, darkvision 60 ft.; Perception +14<br>DEFENSE<br>AC 21, touch 12, flat-footed 19 (+1 Dex, +1 dodge, +9 natural)<br>hp 51 (6d10+18)<br>Fort +8, Ref +6, Will +3<br>Resist electricity 10, fire 10<br>OFFENSE<br>Speed 10 ft., swim 90 ft.<br>Melee bite +9 (1d6+3), 2 claws +9 (1d6+3)<br>Special Attacks ink cloud<br>STATISTICS<br>Str 16, Dex 13, Con 17, Int 10, Wis 12, Cha 9<br>Base Atk +6; CMB +9; CMD 21 (29 vs. trip)<br>Feats Blind-Fight, Dodge, Power Attack<br>Skills Bluff +5, Escape Artist +10, Knowledge (planes) +9, Perception +14, Perform (act) +5, Sense Motive +10, Stealth +7, Survival +7, Swim +11; Racial Modifiers +4 Perception<br>Languages Aquan<br>ECOLOGY<br>Environment any water (Plane of Water)<br>Organization solitary, pair, clutch (3–6), or cult (1 tojanida plus 2–12 humanoid followers)<br>Treasure standard<br>SPECIAL ABILITIES<br>Ink Cloud (Ex) A tojanida can emit a 30-foot-radius sphere of ink once per minute as a free action. The ink provides total concealment in water, and persists for 1 minute. If used out of the water, the jet of ink is a line 30 feet long, and creatures in the area must succeed at a DC 16 Reflex save or be blinded for 1 round.<br>The save DC is Constitution-based. <br><br>Tojanidas are bizarre natives from the Plane of Water that resemble mixes between monstrous crabs and enormous snapping turtles. Originally elemental beings of water, tojanidas were bound into their strange forms long ago for unclear reasons, and no longer know how they might eventually return to their pure and formless state. Determined to preserve their pride, the grotesque tojanidas ply the waters of the planes seeking hedonistic pleasures— especially culinary ones—and the adoration of other races. Loquacious when addressed with the proper respect, they make excellent heralds and emissaries for more powerful beings, and often enjoy posing as such even when operating on their own. When riled, however, tojanidas make fearsome opponents, violent and eager juggernauts with snapping jaws and clacking pincers.<br>Adult tojanidas are roughly 6 feet long and weigh several hundred pounds. When threatened, a tojanida can retract its limbs most of the way into its shell, which is an irremovable part of its body. The ring of eyes completely encircling the tojanida’s shell along its rim makes the creature extremely difficult to catch by surprise. While tojanidas adore eating, as they find f lavor and texture to be two of the most fascinating senses, they don’t actually need to consume food, instead drawing sustenance directly from the currents of arcane energy all around them via the magic of their shells. <br>Blessed (some might say cursed) with extremely long racial memories, tojanidas wander the oceans and lakes of innumerable worlds, attempting to find unusual physical pleasures or conversation capable of distracting them from the insufferable ennui and apathy born of remembering their ancestors’ experiences. Though the tojanidas themselves may not appreciate the burden of memory, adventurers and scholars often seek the use of a tojanida’s recalled lore.</div></div></div></div>
